About | Finance & Operations





















  




Solar Senior Capital’s finance and operations team is led by Richard L. Peteka, Chief Financial Officer and Secretary. The experienced team of eleven professionals provide the company with various experience, including treasury, accounting, financial reporting, compliance, and investor relations support.

